{
  "stem": "24364.4",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I know I went there and said, hey, listen, I want to go to medical school and I just have to pass this test and can you maybe help me how to pass it?",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they always some-- they-- they're lenient and they gave me suggestions and they told me what they're going-- approximately what they're going to ask me on the test.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It was rough.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I studied for 3 months, about 16 hours a day, day after day after day.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I passed.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And in September of '47, I started medical school in Prague.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And in February '48, the Communists came.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I decided I don't want to stay here, because I really didn't have anybody in Czechoslovakia and I wanted to go to-- back to Palestine.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And so I decided I'm going to go to Vienna.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And somehow we managed to get to Vienna.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And I continued in Vienna, and finished in Vienna in '54.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And by that time, I had met my husband.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And we got married in 1955.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And he was still finishing his PhD, and I didn't-- I couldn't practice in Vienna, because I didn't have Austrian citizenship.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "So I-- since we didn't have any money, we were very poor at that time.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "So I went back to Israel at that time and I did my internship in Israel.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And finished medical-- he finished his thesis and got his PhD.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And then I came back and then we came here.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "In the meantime, he had-- even though we really wanted to go to Israel.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "But in the meantime, he had gotten by chance somehow they-- they offered him to go to the United State without a quota, because he was a fugitive from Communism.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And so he took it.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
